Introduction
========================================================
left: 65%
The human memory is far from flawless but most people do not remember everything that has happened to them. It gets stronger the more you use it. But you can't expect it to develop by lifting the same weight every day. You'll need to keep your mind stimulated at all times. This basic face memory game not only enhances your memory, but it also teaches you to pay attention to every single detail. This game promotes critical thinking, which aids in the development of a human's attention to detail. Visual recognition can also be improved by playing memory games.
****  

**Stakeholders**
- Children to train their memory power
- Old people whose memory is slowly fading away
- Parents




