Key Takeaways
========================================================

- A face memory game is a fun way to enhance memory power.
- By setting a time limit, you can challenge yourself to reach new milestones in terms of memory power.
- Memory is crucial to humans and there is no end to the capabilities it has.
- Facial recognition is more effective than object recognition.
- Bad memory could cause conflict and should be improved.